------------------------------------------------------------
Third-Party Components
------------------------------------------------------------

This project uses the following open-source resources,
each distributed under permissive licenses compatible with the MIT License.

Word Lists © respective maintainers  
The following community-maintained word datasets are used for
valid guesses and solution pools. Each is publicly available and
credited for acknowledgment:

• Tab Atkins — Wordle List  
  https://github.com/tabatkins/wordle-list

• DarkerMango — 5-Letter Words  
  https://github.com/DarkerMango/5-Letter-words  
  Raw list: https://darkermango.github.io/5-Letter-words/words.txt

• Charles Reid — five-letter words  
  https://github.com/charlesreid1/five-letter-words (file: sgb-words.txt)

• DWYL — English words  
  https://github.com/dwyl/english-words (file: words_alpha.txt)

These lists are used as public data sources for gameplay logic and are
retrieved dynamically at runtime. They are not modified, redistributed,
or stored beyond the user's browser session.
